## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Operational Layer | Framework Choice | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Frontend Layout** | Next.js 14 (App Router) | React Server Components for zero-latency direct-to-database layout fetches[cite: 1, 1]. |
| **Language Profile** | TypeScript | Strong typing guarantees across component properties, DB models, and API interfaces. |
| **Styling Engine** | Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui | Radix UI accessible, unstyled foundation primitives styled elegantly via Tailwind primitives[cite: 1, 1]. |
| **Database Tier** | PostgreSQL 16 | Relational performance with explicit multi-table primary/foreign constraint links[cite: 1, 1]. |
| **Data Access Client**| Prisma ORM | Deep type-safe query generation, native validation support, and structural migration management[cite: 1, 1]. |
| **Authentication** | NextAuth.js (Credentials Provider) | Internal user authentication with secure bcrypt hashing and JSON Web Token (JWT) role storage[cite: 1, 1]. |
| **Form Management**  | React Hook Form + Zod | Client-side tracking backed by strict, structural schema validators. |
| **State & Fetching**  | TanStack Query (React Query) | High-performance cache controls, background synchronization, and reactive local updates. |

